  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6772.81 sitting below the 6797 flip strike in a PIN regime, dealers are currently long gamma and will be buying this dip while selling any rally toward the massive 6800 wall (65487M GEX). The regime just flipped with a massive GEX surge (2244% in 1-min), creating a strong stabilizing force with multiple positive gamma walls stacked between 6780-6800 that will act as selling pressure on any upside momentum. Watch 6750 as the key support where dealers flip to buying mode, while 6800 becomes the critical resistance where maximum dealer selling pressure kicks in.\n\n**Bottom line:** Expect the market to get pinned between 6750-6800 with mean reversion toward 6785.",
